---
import ScrollReveal from "./ScrollReveal.svelte";
---

<section class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <ScrollReveal client:visible animation="fade-up">
        <p class="mb-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-gold">
          Our Mission
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal client:visible animation="fade-up" delay={150}>
        <h2 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold leading-snug text-navy sm:text-4xl">
          Every Deal Tells a Story.<br />We Make It Tangible.
        </h2>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal client:visible animation="fade-up" delay={300}>
        <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate/80">
          Behind every closed deal is a team that worked late nights, navigated complexity, and made it happen. ABC Deal Toys creates premium commemorative pieces that capture the magnitude of those moments — not just as trophies, but as stories cast in crystal, metal, and glass.
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>
      <ScrollReveal client:visible animation="fade-up" delay={450}>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate/80">
          From billion-dollar mergers to milestone fund closings, we've helped firms across Wall Street and beyond celebrate the people who make deals happen. Because closers deserve more than a handshake.
        </p>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
